ComparisonPage_LimitedLayouts - Text for limited layouts in trial
ComparisonPage_UnlimitedLayouts - Text for unlimited layouts in PRO
ComparisonPage_CanvasSize - Row header for canvas size
ComparisonPage_SmallCanvas - Text for small canvas in free plan
ComparisonPage_MediumCanvas - Text for medium canvas in trial
ComparisonPage_LargeCanvas - Text for large canvas in PRO
ComparisonPage_SpecsSheets - Row header for specs sheets
ComparisonPage_LimitedSpecs - Text for limited specs in free plan
ComparisonPage_BasicSpecs - Text for basic specs in trial
ComparisonPage_FullSpecs - Text for full specs in PRO
ComparisonPage_ExportOptions - Row header for export options
